<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.1.9">
<l>uḷaṉeṉi luḷaṉava ṉuruvamiv vuruvuka</l>
<l>ḷuḷaṉala ṉeṉilava ṉaruvamiv varuvuka</l>
<l>ḷuḷaṉeṉa vilaṉeṉa vivaikuṇa muṭaimaiyi</l>
<l>luḷaṉiru takaimaiyo ṭoḻivilaṉ parantē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one says “he exists”, the form of him who exists is these forms,</l>
<l>if one says “he does not exist”, his non-form is these non-forms.</l>
<l>In the possession of these as qualities: “he is” or “he is not”,</l>
<l>he is with two qualities, spreading he is without end.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
